="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="d64fe93d-6ac1-4756-aa03-f1857c441f85" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3-mini" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="142">Creo que te refieres a <strong data-start="23" data-end="51">“sealed” en programación</strong>, sobre todo en lenguajes como <strong data-start="82" data-end="92">Kotlin</strong> o también conceptos similares en otros lenguajes.</p>
<h3 data-start="144" data-end="173"><span role="text">¿Para qué sirve <code data-start="164" data-end="172">sealed</code>?</span></h3>
<p data-start="175" data-end="340">Una <strong data-start="179" data-end="207">clase <code data-start="187" data-end="195">sealed</code> (sellada)</strong> se usa para <strong data-start="220" data-end="256">restringir quién puede heredarla</strong>. Es decir, defines una clase base pero controlas exactamente qué subclases existen.</p>
<h3 data-start="342" data-end="369">En Kotlin, por ejemplo:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="371" data-end="492"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Kotlin</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">sealed</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Result</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Success</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼn">val</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">data</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">String</span><span>) : </span><span class="ͼt">Result</span><span>()</span><br><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Error</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼn">val</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">message</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">String</span><span>) : </span><span class="ͼt">Result</span><span>()</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="494" data-end="517">¿Qué ventaja tiene?</h3>
<ul data-start="519" data-end="696">
<li data-start="519" data-end="618">
<p data-start="521" data-end="618">🔒 <strong data-start="524" data-end="558">Control total de las subclases</strong>: solo las que defines en el mismo archivo pueden heredarla.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="619" data-end="696">
<p data-start="621" data-end="696">🧠 <strong data-start="624" data-end="651">Mejor manejo con <code data-start="643" data-end="649">when</code></strong>: el compilador sabe todas las posibilidades.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="698" data-end="837"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Kotlin</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">fun</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">handle</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">result</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">Result</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">when</span><span> (</span><span class="ͼt">result</span><span>) {</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">is</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Success</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">-&gt;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">println</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">result</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼn">data</span><span>)</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">is</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Error</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">-&gt;</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">println</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">result</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼt">message</span><span>)</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="839" data-end="915">👉 Aquí no necesitas <code data-start="860" data-end="866">else</code>, porque el compilador ya conoce todos los casos.</p>
<h3 data-start="917" data-end="953">¿Para qué se usa en la práctica?</h3>
<ul data-start="955" data-end="1089">
<li data-start="955" data-end="990">
<p data-start="957" data-end="990">Estados (loading, success, error)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="991" data-end="1010">
<p data-start="993" data-end="1010">Resultados de API</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1011" data-end="1045">
<p data-start="1013" data-end="1045">Modelar flujos cerrados de datos</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1046" data-end="1089">
<p data-start="1048" data-end="1089">Reducir errores por casos no contemplados</p>
</li>
