<p data-start="414" data-end="432">👉 Eso rompe todo.</p>
<p data-start="434" data-end="497">✔ Debe estar <strong data-start="447" data-end="475">fuera de cualquier clase</strong>, a nivel del archivo:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="499" data-end="701"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Kotlin</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">sealed</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Animal</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Perro</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼn">val</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">nombre</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">String</span><span>) : </span><span class="ͼt">Animal</span><span>()</span><br><span class="ͼn">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Gato</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼn">val</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">nombre</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">String</span><span>) : </span><span class="ͼt">Animal</span><span>()</span><br><span class="ͼn">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">Pajaro</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼn">val</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">especie</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">String</span><span>) : </span><span class="ͼt">Animal</span><span>()</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="703" data-end="706">
<h2 data-start="708" data-end="770">🚨 2. El archivo está mal configurado o en sitio incorrecto</h2>
<p data-start="772" data-end="790">Asegúrate de esto:</p>
<ul data-start="792" data-end="883">
<li data-start="792" data-end="831">
<p data-start="794" data-end="831">📁 Está en <code data-start="805" data-end="820">src/main/java</code> o <code data-start="823" data-end="831">kotlin</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="832" data-end="883">
<p data-start="834" data-end="883">📦 Tiene package correcto (o ninguno para probar)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="885" data-end="902">Ejemplo correcto:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="904" data-end="957"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Kotlin</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">package</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">com</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼt">ejemplo</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼt">app</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="959" data-end="962">
<h2 data-start="964" data-end="1009">🚨 3. Estás viendo error por caché del IDE</h2>
<p data-start="1011" data-end="1055">Haz esto (muy importante en Android Studio):</p>
<ul data-start="1057" data-end="1147">
<li data-start="1057" data-end="1082">
<p data-start="1059" data-end="1082">Build → Clean Project</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1083" data-end="1110">
<p data-start="1085" data-end="1110">Build → Rebuild Project</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1111" data-end="1147">
<p data-start="1113" data-end="1147">File → Invalidate Caches / Restart</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1149" data-end="1152">
<h2 data-start="1154" data-end="1196">🚨 4. El error NO es del código (clave)</h2>
<p data-start="1198" data-end="1278">Si aún falla, necesito el <strong data-start="1224" data-end="1250">mensaje exacto en rojo</strong>, porque ahí está la verdad.</p>
<p data-start="1280" data-end="1313">Ejemplos de errores que importan:</p>
<ul data-start="1314" data-end="1409">
<li data-start="1314" data-end="1349">
<p data-start="1316" data-end="1349">“expecting top level declaration”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1350" data-end="1367">
<p data-start="1352" data-end="1367">“redeclaration”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1368" data-end="1402">
<p data-start="1370" data-end="1402">“sealed modifier is not allowed”</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1403" data-end="1409">
<p data-start="1405" data-end="1409">etc.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1411" data-end="1414">
<h2 data-start="1416" data-end="1437">💡 Resumen honesto</h2>
<p data-start="1439" data-end="1569">👉 Tu código está correcto<br data-start="1465" data-end="1468">
👉 El problema es el contexto del proyecto o el IDE<br data-start="1519" data-end="1522">
👉 Sin el error exacto, es imposible afinar más</p>
