<hr data-start="116" data-end="119">
<h1 data-start="121" data-end="156">🔵 Por qué “main no sale en azul”</h1>
<p data-start="158" data-end="174">Depende de esto:</p>
<h2 data-start="176" data-end="227">1. ❌ No tienes el plugin de Scala bien instalado</h2>
<p data-start="228" data-end="305">Si usas IntelliJ o VS Code sin configuración correcta, <code data-start="283" data-end="290">@main</code> no se resalta.</p>
<hr data-start="307" data-end="310">
<h2 data-start="312" data-end="355">2. ❌ Estás en un archivo que no es Scala</h2>
<p data-start="356" data-end="370">Tiene que ser:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="371" data-end="396"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>archivo.scala</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="398" data-end="441">Si es <code data-start="404" data-end="410">.txt</code>, <code data-start="412" data-end="419">.java</code>, etc., no lo detecta.</p>
<hr data-start="443" data-end="446">
<h2 data-start="448" data-end="494">3. ❌ Falta configuración del proyecto Scala</h2>
<p data-start="495" data-end="561">Si no tienes sbt/Scala configurado, el editor no entiende <code data-start="553" data-end="560">@main</code>.</p>
<hr data-start="563" data-end="566">
<h2 data-start="568" data-end="617">4. ⚠️ Estás esperando “color = funcionamiento”</h2>
<p data-start="618" data-end="699">El color <strong data-start="627" data-end="652">NO afecta al programa</strong>.<br data-start="653" data-end="656">
Aunque no esté azul, puede funcionar igual.</p>
<hr data-start="701" data-end="704">
<h1 data-start="706" data-end="721">🧠 IMPORTANTE</h1>
<p data-start="723" data-end="820">👉 <code data-start="726" data-end="733">@main</code> <strong data-start="734" data-end="773">NO necesita ser azul para funcionar</strong><br data-start="773" data-end="776">
👉 Solo necesita estar escrito correctamente</p>
