<h2 data-start="186" data-end="217">✅ Opción 1: atajo de teclado</h2>
<ul data-start="218" data-end="272">
<li data-start="218" data-end="251">
<p data-start="220" data-end="251"><strong data-start="220" data-end="240">Windows / Linux:</strong> <code data-start="241" data-end="251">Ctrl + S</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="252" data-end="272">
<p data-start="254" data-end="272"><strong data-start="254" data-end="262">Mac:</strong> <code data-start="263" data-end="272">Cmd + S</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="274" data-end="315">👉 Esto guarda el archivo inmediatamente.</p>
<hr data-start="317" data-end="320">
<h2 data-start="322" data-end="341">✅ Opción 2: menú</h2>
<ol data-start="342" data-end="447">
<li data-start="342" data-end="387">
<p data-start="345" data-end="387">Arriba a la izquierda → <strong data-start="369" data-end="387">File (Archivo)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="388" data-end="447">
<p data-start="391" data-end="447">Click en <strong data-start="400" data-end="418">Save (Guardar)</strong> o <strong data-start="421" data-end="447">Save As (Guardar como)</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="449" data-end="452">
<h2 data-start="454" data-end="470">⚠️ IMPORTANTE</h2>
<p data-start="472" data-end="508">Si es la primera vez que lo guardas:</p>
<ul data-start="509" data-end="581">
<li data-start="509" data-end="527">
<p data-start="511" data-end="527">te pedirá nombre</p>
</li>
<li data-start="528" data-end="581">
<p data-start="530" data-end="581">asegúrate de poner extensión correcta, por ejemplo:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="583" data-end="624"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Main.scala</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="626" data-end="629">
<h1 data-start="631" data-end="654">🧠 CONSEJO PARA SCALA</h1>
<p data-start="656" data-end="684">Cuando guardes código Scala:</p>
<p data-start="686" data-end="743">✔ archivo debe terminar en <code data-start="713" data-end="721">.scala</code><br data-start="721" data-end="724">
✔ ejemplo correcto:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="745" data-end="790"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Pedidos.scala</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="792" data-end="795">
<h1 data-start="797" data-end="837">💻 Si estás en Visual Studio (no Code)</h1>
<ol data-start="839" data-end="939">
<li data-start="839" data-end="871">
<p data-start="842" data-end="871"><code data-start="842" data-end="852">Ctrl + S</code> también funciona</p>
</li>
<li data-start="872" data-end="890">
<p data-start="875" data-end="890">O File → Save</p>
</li>
<li data-start="891" data-end="939">
<p data-start="894" data-end="939">Pero Visual Studio <strong data-start="913" data-end="939">no es bueno para Scala</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="941" data-end="944">
<h1 data-start="946" data-end="963">🚨 ERROR TÍPICO</h1>
<p data-start="965" data-end="980">❌ Guardar como:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="981" data-end="1019"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-0da2cb3c.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>archivo.txt</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1021" data-end="1044">👉 eso NO ejecuta Scala</p>
<hr data-start="1046" data-end="1049">
<h1 data-start="1051" data-end="1063">🔥 RESUMEN</h1>
<ul data-start="1065" data-end="1178">
<li data-start="1065" data-end="1099">
<p data-start="1067" data-end="1099">💾 <code data-start="1070" data-end="1080">Ctrl + S</code> = guardar rápido</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1100" data-end="1132">
<p data-start="1102" data-end="1132">📁 archivo debe ser <code data-start="1122" data-end="1130">.scala</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1133" data-end="1178">
<p data-start="1135" data-end="1178">▶️ guardar ≠ ejecutar (son cosas distintas)</p>
</li>
</ul>
